{"tid":84724,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［公投］戴錶戴左手定右手","createTime":"2017-01-17T17:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T05:36:15.000Z","uid":40286,"like":212,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f80afadc0deff2840340666ed8c01beec03a23d","tid":84724,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"左手：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n右手：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86188d2af9f5f517ce6523f0da58f33b342b512","tid":84724,"uid":58724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:44:34.000Z","msg":"左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e8cee7837fc1920f356503dd4516fbc7fe9cda","tid":84724,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:48:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4ee8b06253c1964ba5ebde5b59148ab607b4aed","tid":84724,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:48:18.000Z","msg":"其實好似未見過人戴右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6138d28ed16398122909e77588f81a09cd8b26","tid":84724,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:50:22.000Z","msg":"細個覺得要戴右手，因為寫字揸筷子都係右手，所以右手叻啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後發現個個都戴左手，同發現頂住寫字，就戴返左手<br />\n但右手唔多識幫左手戴錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd26f7a64d63f27977661d9a2973b012ba2bc15f","tid":84724,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個覺得要戴右手，因為寫字揸筷子都係右手，所以右手叻啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後發現個個都戴左手，同發現頂住寫字，就戴返左手<br />\n但右手唔多識幫左手戴錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日要拍隻手埋個肚到戴 費事跌錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6243d4e220443d052bf96dfda1aab5432c8237","tid":84724,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:51:39.000Z","msg":"左<br />\n其實有d錶係for右手"},{"pid":"84932cf41c1cd0ab7161b4b12222386358c4754b","tid":84724,"uid":55281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個覺得要戴右手，因為寫字揸筷子都係右手，所以右手叻啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後發現個個都戴左手，同發現頂住寫字，就戴返左手<br />\n但右手唔多識幫左手戴錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係見個個都左手就轉左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1305723518a2cc7a4f8b9a9f0e2a17e9b470a9a","tid":84724,"uid":77102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:52:46.000Z","msg":"左拗先會戴右手，有幾個fd都係"},{"pid":"4defc71fa2ff4ab0e847852656e4dc522c353f05","tid":84724,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左<br />\n其實有d錶係for右手</blockquote><br />\n真係未見過 願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d3a9a47b0aa24ebf3d4fdbffe893a7a7553ead","tid":84724,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左拗先會戴右手，有幾個fd都係</blockquote><br />\n手邊嘅左拗朋友都會跟風戴左 有啲索性唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a53ef5de6d4ee5cb088c95742f83110865b25d","tid":84724,"uid":65875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好似未見過人戴右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我帶右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我左手寫字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0279f1e481a46f39b63f4c10a708e366217045c","tid":84724,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:57:15.000Z","msg":"請問係咪根據番隻錶粒把的黎決定左定右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e35059a46c048cba4c5ff96054fb389707b84b3","tid":84724,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:57:36.000Z","msg":"當盾牌用你話戴邊隻手"},{"pid":"e50d56b8560a48db53ec6cc17127bb076c2e51a5","tid":84724,"uid":4293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:58:56.000Z","msg":"右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n右手寫字揸筷子"},{"pid":"40c3b730473c7749cf2e17f2ea4eb6e2b7319f52","tid":84724,"uid":10579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"由細到大都係戴右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己都唔知點解，身邊朋友得我係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 用右手寫字"},{"pid":"c2b36876ecd2f38febd9fffd0c80444604ae0468","tid":84724,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T18:05:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>左<br />\n其實有d錶係for右手</blockquote><br />\n真係未見過 願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個crown應該向住隻手<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.watchonista.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/watchonista_v1_560x560/watchographer/1061/watches/1981_tudor_oyster_prince_submariner_left_94010_soldat_300dpi_square.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.watchonista.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimagecache%2Fwatchonista_v1_560x560%2Fwatchographer%2F1061%2Fwatches%2F1981_tudor_oyster_prince_submariner_left_94010_soldat_300dpi_square.jpg&h=f16cf3f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8117dd1a90f1b6ffa2504837c6eb45fbb124b2a1","tid":84724,"uid":6577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T18:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左拗先會戴右手，有幾個fd都係</blockquote><br />\n我左拗都戴左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc7e31deb92cb1a5ea032d8f4c587ce2493f623","tid":84724,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T18:37:21.000Z","msg":"都係個句啦，男左女右。<br />\nbut有啲錶係專for右手，for你潛水，做運動果啲"},{"pid":"28e03b622df0bf011b76a9be712424ee0c69e6ff","tid":84724,"uid":56727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:07:18.000Z","msg":"右<br />\n利申:右拗"},{"pid":"3b514b9301ad5f433cf07f6ea5c9e9663895bcd6","tid":84724,"uid":56727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:07:42.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"775bfd0dfc952abfa63486a6ed54b55ae39897c0","tid":84724,"uid":22984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:09:28.000Z","msg":"右"},{"pid":"88babab4cfb7a42a76ca76f3b5f292d33af6981e","tid":84724,"uid":72801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>左拗先會戴右手，有幾個fd都係</blockquote><br />\n我左拗都戴左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戴右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5df8c99026e47e0e6716811d9b9b473a34b46b","tid":84724,"uid":16914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:41:33.000Z","msg":"我帶兩隻錶。"},{"pid":"7a3273ec49ffb62d04098fde6c1ed4b670da13d8","tid":84724,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:51:21.000Z","msg":"右手寫字帶右手，我老豆都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我左半邊身真係好唔靈活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  慣左所有重要野都係擺晒係右邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}